title: (PSX-PSP) Heart of Darkness converted properly (Kingdom-games by
description:
HEART OF DARKNESS:

Andy and his dog, Whisky, are out in the park having a good time. Suddenly, a solar eclipse occurs, and Whisky disappears. Andy jumps into his homemade space ship and travels to another world to save his dog. As one would expect, Andy encounters some resistance and crash lands on the planet. You will take control of Andy as he travels through eight unique worlds in search of his companion. Each world is divided into a series of puzzles, some of which require blasting enemies with the plasma cannon, while others require running and jumping. After solving several puzzles, the player is treated to beautiful video sequences that congratulate the player and advance the story. Whisky needs to be saved, and Andy is the only person who can do it in HEART OF DARKNESS.

Tested and working properly on CFW 5.00 m33-4 combined with the 500 popsloader pack on 3.72 POPS....KloWn
